Creates a new member definition.

Parameters
dfFile containing the definition of this member.
dlLine at which the member definition was found.
dcColumn at which the member definition was found.
tA string representing the type of the member.
naA string representing the name of the member.
aA string representing the arguments of the member.
eA string representing the throw clause of the members.
pThe protection context of the member, possible values are: Public, Protected, Private.
vThe degree of 'virtualness' of the member, possible values are: Normal, Virtual, Pure.
sA boolean that is true iff the member is static.
rThe relationship between the class and the member.
mtThe kind of member. See MemberType for a list of all types.
talThe template arguments of this member.
alThe arguments of this member. This is a structured form of the string past as argument a.
metaSlice metadata.

1956 // private *documented* virtual members are shown if EXTRACT_PRIV_VIRTUAL
1957 // is set to YES
1958 bool visibleIfPrivate = (protectionLevelVisible(protection()) ||
1959 m_impl->mtype==MemberType_Friend ||
1960 (m_impl->prot==Protection::Private &&
1961 (m_impl->virt!=Specifier::Normal || isOverride() || isFinal()) && extractPrivateVirtual && hasDocs)
1962 );
1963
1964 // hide member if it overrides a member in a superclass and has no
1965 // documentation of its own
1966 //bool visibleIfDocVirtual = !reimplements() ||
1967 // !Config_getBool(INHERIT_DOCS) ||
1968 // hasDocs;
1969
1970 // true if this member is a constructor or destructor
1971 bool cOrDTor = isConstructor() || isDestructor();
1972
1973 // hide default constructors or destructors (no args) without
1974 // documentation
1975 bool visibleIfNotDefaultCDTor = !(cOrDTor &&
1976 (m_impl->defArgList.empty() ||
1977 m_impl->defArgList.front().type == "void"
1978 ) &&
1979 !hasDocs
1980 );
1981
1982
1983 //printf("visibleIfStatic=%d visibleIfDocumented=%d visibleIfEnabled=%d "
1984 // "visibleIfPrivate=%d visibleIfNotDefaultCDTor=%d "
1985 // "visibleIfFriendCompound=%d !annScope=%d\n",
1986 // visibleIfStatic,visibleIfDocumented,
1987 // visibleIfEnabled,visibleIfPrivate,visibleIfNotDefaultCDTor,
1988 // visibleIfFriendCompound,!m_impl->annScope);
1989
1990 bool visible = visibleIfStatic && visibleIfDocumented &&
1991 visibleIfEnabled && visibleIfPrivate &&
1992 /*visibleIfDocVirtual &&*/ visibleIfNotDefaultCDTor &&
1993 visibleIfFriendCompound &&
1994 !m_impl->annScope && !isHidden();
1995 //printf("MemberDefImpl::isBriefSectionVisible() %d\n",visible);
1996 return visible;
